What you’re actually building (clean frame)

You’re building a Pattern Library + Reinstantiation Engine:
	1.	Observe
	•	Notice something working (design, persuasion, systems, etc.)
	2.	Extract
	•	Strip it to its invariant (what must be true for it to work)
	3.	Compress
	•	Turn it into a prompt / schema / rule
	4.	Reinstantiate
	•	Apply it in a different domain
	5.	Test
	•	Does it still work without you there?
	6.	Store (Money Bin)
	•	Only keep what survives

That’s a legit engine.

