The one guardrail you need (this matters)

Not every pattern that feels powerful is actually real.

So add a simple filter:

“Did this produce an external, measurable effect?”

Examples of real signals:
	•	Someone else uses it
	•	It improves an outcome (clicks, clarity, speed, decisions)
	•	It works in a different domain
	•	It still works when simplified

If not → it’s still in sandbox / hypothesis mode

